{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回「疑云起」：程垓与黄公绍逃入废宅，发现玉剑萧凌病卧。追忆前晚，二人在相府被残金毒掌追赶，与孙清羽、孙琪一同被诱出。残金毒掌欲杀三人，却独放孙琪。黄公绍与程垓趁隙逃走，残金毒掌追至废宅，一掌击毙黄公绍，却饶程垓一命。程垓历经生死，幡然醒悟。正欲离去，相国公子古浊飘携书僮棋儿到访，程垓解释经过。古浊飘查看尸身，发现并无金色掌印，程垓大惑。棋儿展示各派武功。回相府后，棋儿以话激程垓比武，以武当小擒拿手、少林洪拳对程垓的落叶追风掌，最终以昆仑惊鸿掠树制胜。程垓认输羞愧离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "一人（程垓或黄公绍）",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这是一栋废宅呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "另一人（程垓或黄公绍）",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这最好也没有了，我们在这里躲一阵再说，再跑我可受不了啦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "同一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道孙家的叔侄两人怎样了，据我看，十成里有九成是没命了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "另一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这魔头真的名不虚传，不说别的，单是身法之快，我简直见都没有见过，喂，你有火折子没有，点上看看再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里真是一个人也没有，只希望那魔头不要找来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那边好像有人的声音。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听来像是个女子的声音，莫非是受了什么伤？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看，这里居然还有人在，这女人的呻吟之声，也是由那里发出的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这不是玉剑萧凌吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧姑娘怎会跑到这里来了？看样子不是受了伤，就是病倒了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_gong_shao",
      "speaker_name": "黄公绍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们别再管人家的事了，眼看着我们自己也是自身难保呢！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "退出去。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "相好的，是好朋友留下来亮亮相，别藏头露尾的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追丢了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人影不知是哪一路朋友，身法好快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "别着急，我看那人是存心诱我们进去，我们不追也没有关系，只是那人身手太高，我们四人千万不能失散，最好能一致行动。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "残金毒掌。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "残金毒掌",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "姓孙的，你也没死呀。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "text": "一别二十年，阁下仍是如此，故人不老，真叫我孙清羽高兴得很，只是阁下将在下等召来此处，有何见教？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "残金毒掌",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "要你的命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "text": "孤独大侠二十年不见，依然还是老脾气，故友重逢，俱都无恙，应当高兴才是，就算是要区区在下的命，也不必忙在一时呀。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "残金毒掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们三个人留下来，那个年轻的混蛋给我快滚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_sun_qi",
      "text": "琪儿走吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孙琪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还我哥哥的命来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_jin_du_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "残金毒掌",
      "listener": "char_sun_qi",
      "text": "滚开。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我惟一该走的路，就是隐姓埋名，抱头一忍，唉，凭我这一点浅薄的武功，还有什么资格在武林中争胜？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蜘蛛都如此，难道我连这蜘蛛还不如吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世上还有许多事，是我该做的呀！我欠了人家的，我也该去一一补偿，埋头一走，岂是大丈夫行径？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "房外人（古浊飘）",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜！可惜！这大好房间，却被如此荒废了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "房外人（古浊飘）",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棋儿，你看这足迹像是新的，难道屋子里还有人居住吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我进去看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "相公，快进来呀，屋子里有个死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "房外人（古浊飘）",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程大侠怎会跑到这里来了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这不是黄大侠吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程大侠，这到底是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无怪残金毒掌纵横百年，未遇敌手，人家那分绝世的武功呀，真叫人口服心服。",
      "tone": "佩服",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "真的如此吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子若是不信，在下也实无他话解释……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子如果还有不信的地方，在下倒有一个方法让公子相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噢。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄大侠被残金毒掌一掌击中前胸，胸前定必有金色掌印，那不就……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么回事，这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "我和黄公绍乃多年至交，公子若怀疑……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程大侠以为我在怀疑阁下吗？那就错了，兄弟虽然不会武功，但是看总是还看得出一点。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子也会武功吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在才知道呀？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "幼从庭训，读书不忘学剑。只是这些粗浅的功夫，怎入得了方家的法眼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "原来公子也是武林一派，小的倒真走了眼呢。不知公子是何门何派，是否可使在下一开茅塞？",
      "tone": "惶恐",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这你教我们公子怎么说呢？我们公子的老师有嵩山少林寺的玄空上人、武当山上的灵机道长、昆仑派的钟先生，还有云南点苍的七手神剑谢老剑客呢！你说我们公子该算是哪一门哪一派的呀？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿，你不相信是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一下你可相信了吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "在下有眼无珠，竟然不知道公子是位高人。",
      "tone": "惶恐",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "不但公子，就连这位小管家，也是位武林高手呢！",
      "tone": "惶恐",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "真的吗？喂，我们两人来比划比划好不好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "棋儿，不要顽皮。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "黄大侠尸骨暴露此处，总是不妥，不如先抬到寒舍再择吉安葬。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "固所愿也，不敢请耳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程大侠倒是文武全材呢！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程兄如无事，不妨再在寒舍将息几日。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我下半生应该做些什么呢？我还能够做什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "小哥儿，你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程师傅，亏你自称是什么八步赶蝉，我以为你轻功一定是很好的，哪知我跟在你后面多时，你竟丝毫不曾发觉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "小哥儿，你的公子是不是时常传授你武功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我家公子并不曾真正的传授过我一套完整的拳法或剑法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "那你怎会懂得武功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "我家公子练武的时候，我在旁观看，不是就可以学得了吗？程师傅，你的轻功是跟谁学的，怎会如此没用，看来你的师父本领也是有限的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "并不是我师父本领不好，而是我学不到，我的师父名叫赤成子，你一定没有听说过。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赤成子，这名字很熟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程师傅，听说你的落叶追风掌非常厉害，我倒想请教几招！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "小哥儿，我并不是不想陪你走几招，只是，较招这一层，如果有什么错失之处，那可是重则丧命，轻则受伤，我们不如谈谈吧！我说个故事给你听。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不，我不想听故事，我听说落叶追风掌是虚有其名的掌法，练起来虽然很好看，但和敌人对起掌来，却丝毫没有什么用处，因此，我便想和你走几招，看看究竟有没有用场？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "小哥儿，你说落叶追风掌虚有其表也可以，说落叶追风掌有实用也可以，我以为你还是静下来，听我说个故事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程师傅，如果你不发招，那我便认定你的落叶追风掌是没有用的了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "好吧！我就和你走几招，你先发招吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "程师傅，我是主你是客，照礼仪上我应该让你先发招的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我猜得不错，原来所谓闻名武林的落叶追风掌，也不过如是，怎能和残金毒掌相比！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "这一招比刚才较为好一点，仍然看我的！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "程师傅，我早说过你的这套落叶追风掌是没有什么用场的，现在事实摆在眼前，果真如此！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "好小子，你竟敢对我这般侮辱！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！使得好！这才算有点劲味！不然就算不得是江湖上的成名人物了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好掌法！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "这就是昆仑派的惊鸿掠树了，你大概没有见过吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_gai",
      "speaker_name": "程垓",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "棋儿，你本领胜过我，我认输便是！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，你为什么走？我们还没打完呢！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    }
  ],
